OL,12,FTwenty-four hours after the game
OL,13,Flaunched, 'Sker Ritual' by video game
OL,14,Fdevelopers Wales Interactive, was the
OL,15,Fsecond most downloaded game in PC
OL,16,Fcharts.
OL,18,FThe game takes inspiration from the
OL,19,Ftales of 'Sker House', just outside
