OL,7,FDescribed as 'an intense, round-based,
OL,8,Fzombie horror' game, players must
OL,9,Fsolve 'mysterious missions', while
OL,10,Ffacing 'relentless waves' of the Quiet
OL,11,FOnes. But, in a Welsh twist, players
OL,12,Fmust attempt to obtain 'miracles', a
OL,13,Fvast network of Celtic God powers.
OL,15,FDr David Banner, co-founder of Wales
OL,16,FInteractive said: "You make things
OL,17,Fthat resonate with you and I can tell
OL,18,Fyou that in the game industry there
OL,19,Faren't many Welsh people making games.
