OL,7,F"You can play it all in Welsh. We've
OL,8,Fbeen banging the drum supporting the
OL,9,FWelsh language for twelve years. It's
OL,10,Fsomething really important to us cause
OL,11,Fwe're based in Wales and we want to
OL,12,Freflect the area we're in and the
OL,13,Fculture."
OL,15,FThe Welsh inspiration does not end
OL,16,Fthere, as the game includes what the
OL,17,Fdevelopers refer to as 'haunted hymns'.
